{"tid":2295110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大埔靈糧堂劉梅軒中學一名中六學生初步確診","createTime":"2020-11-21T13:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T14:37:49.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"15fd8396818ac0ffb812ec139e0d61b7b5152d46","tid":2295110,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:32:04.000Z","msg":"大埔靈糧堂劉梅軒中學一名中六學生初步確診<br />\n<br />\n大埔靈糧堂劉梅軒中學一名中六學生初步確診新型肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n校方在網頁表示，下午收到該名學生通知初步確診，而該學生最後回校上課為昨日，亦有參與昨日下午的補課。<br />\n<br />\n校方說已啟動緊急事故應變小組，即時開會商討各項跟進，並等待教育局及衞生防護中心的正式通知及具體建議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561238-20201121.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561238-20201121.htm&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r%2FUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=cac37929\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561238-20201121.htm&h=3ba590da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561238-20201121.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9d96b1e4ac49434ff178b415898612f887ab5002","tid":2295110,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"🐤"},{"pid":"a85f1b00518d58ebca3242d7a93a2b2d16583a5a","tid":2295110,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:33:08.000Z","msg":"好快中學都停課<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9547cb5df56a313cefd1060f47da7f8a71e051e2","tid":2295110,"uid":358522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:36:13.000Z","msg":"之後又可以強制檢測啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afad9deacc9dd0bb5428aa2b3fe198a5834ec562","tid":2295110,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:46:48.000Z","msg":"1cm<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />》》<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bou